00:01:38.280 --> 00:01:39.810
Now the entire Macau

00:01:39.810 --> 00:01:41.289
has been completely blockaded

00:01:41.289 --> 00:01:42.560
by the Japanese.

00:01:42.900 --> 00:01:44.759
The fleet can't leave at all now.

00:01:44.900 --> 00:01:47.539
Besides, the shipment is enormous.

00:01:47.810 --> 00:01:49.450
Just unloading them

00:01:49.450 --> 00:01:51.009
took 2 whole days.

00:01:52.920 --> 00:01:54.070
With so little time,

00:01:55.259 --> 00:01:57.320
how could we possibly
transport everything?

00:01:57.320 --> 00:01:58.650
Even if we could,

00:01:58.759 --> 00:02:00.430
Macau is tiny.

00:02:01.000 --> 00:02:01.930
Is there a building or a street

00:02:01.930 --> 00:02:03.290
that the Sawa Agency doesn't know?

00:02:03.290 --> 00:02:04.950
