What Xian means is that

00:02:08.410 --> 00:02:10.960
everyone should immediately gather
all available manpower

00:02:10.960 --> 00:02:13.340
and seize as much of the supplies
as possible.

00:02:13.340 --> 00:02:14.400
As for where to hide it,

00:02:14.400 --> 00:02:15.910
he's already working on a solution.

00:02:15.910 --> 00:02:17.170
What kind of solution?

00:02:17.360 --> 00:02:18.340
Xian said

00:02:18.340 --> 00:02:19.840
that for now, the only option

00:02:19.840 --> 00:02:22.130
is to take another risk
and use the blind spot

00:02:22.130 --> 00:02:23.530
right under their noses.

00:02:25.680 --> 00:02:26.370
Xian?

00:02:27.860 --> 00:02:29.310
Why did you need to see me so urgently?

00:02:29.310 --> 00:02:29.910
Hongshen,

00:02:30.150 --> 00:02:31.710
I don't have time to explain.

00:02:31.710 --> 00:02:33.150
I need to use the Lyun Coeng warehouse

00:02:33.150 --> 00:02:34.030
you're in charge of.

00:02:34.030 --> 00:02:34.910
And this matter

00:02:34.910 --> 00:02:35.840
must remain secret

00:02:35.840 --> 00:02:38.040
from everyone in Lyun Coeng except you.

00:02:49.690 --> 00:02:50.530
Guys!

00:02:50.530 --> 00:02:52.150
Move it!

00:02:52.190 --> 00:02:53.870
-Move!
-Hurry up!

00:03:08.900 --> 00:03:09.810
Be careful!

00:03:10.680 --> 00:03:11.470
Let's go!

00:03:27.340 --> 00:03:28.150
What's wrong?

00:03:28.930 --> 00:03:29.930
Feeling guilty?

00:03:32.260 --> 00:03:33.260
Chief,

00:03:33.280 --> 00:03:36.440
I've heard that Consul Imai
is a veteran spy.

00:03:36.460 --> 00:03:38.860
He's spent most of his life
working in China

00:03:39.630 --> 00:03:41.750
and has headed
several intelligence agencies.

00:03:41.750 --> 00:03:42.970
With his experience,

00:03:43.130 --> 00:03:45.600
if he actually connects
with the Portuguese Macau government

00:03:45.600 --> 00:03:46.660
and spots our flaw,

00:03:46.690 --> 00:03:49.030
we may lose control of the situation.

00:03:49.960 --> 00:03:52.900
Then let's just not let him connect

00:03:52.930 --> 00:03:55.130
with the Portuguese Macau government.

00:03:55.780 --> 00:03:56.960
Not let him connect?

00:03:58.170 --> 00:03:59.980
I know Imai well.

00:04:00.540 --> 00:04:02.370
He is an experienced spy
and a China expert.

00:04:02.370 --> 00:04:03.210
That's true.

00:04:04.310 --> 00:04:05.970
But aside from his seniority,

00:04:06.650 --> 00:04:10.160
he's actually foolish and timid,

00:04:10.690 --> 00:04:12.940
a complete incompetent person.

00:04:14.210 --> 00:04:15.090
Otherwise,

00:04:15.970 --> 00:04:19.540
why would I recommend him
to serve as consul in Macau?

00:04:35.930 --> 00:04:37.659
[Liu Jike's Egg Cake]

00:04:48.290 --> 00:04:49.140
Mr. Imai,

00:04:49.990 --> 00:04:50.580
are you aware
that the Portuguese Macau government

00:04:50.580 --> 00:04:53.240
[Imai Keiichi,
the New Japanese Consul in Macau]

00:04:53.240 --> 00:04:56.500
is the prime suspect
in the assassination of Consul Fukue?

00:04:56.560 --> 00:04:57.360
What?

00:04:58.060 --> 00:05:00.660
The previous cargo ship attack
was carried out

00:05:00.830 --> 00:05:02.570
by the Portuguese Macau government

00:05:02.570 --> 00:05:05.030
in secret collusion
with the Allied Forces.

00:05:05.430 --> 00:05:06.990
Mr. Fukue was outraged

00:05:07.430 --> 00:05:09.690
and intended to recommend to the Command

00:05:10.020 --> 00:05:12.330
that Macau be occupied by force.

00:05:13.070 --> 00:05:13.810
However,

00:05:14.680 --> 00:05:17.740
we didn't expect
that just after he left the consulate,

00:05:18.000 --> 00:05:20.430
he would be killed by a masked assassin.

00:05:21.860 --> 00:05:22.830
So if this wasn't

00:05:23.430 --> 00:05:25.960
the work
of the Portuguese Macau government,

00:05:26.810 --> 00:05:28.340
who else could it have been?

00:05:30.190 --> 00:05:31.160
I see.

00:05:31.720 --> 00:05:34.050
So that's why Mr. Fukue was assassinated.

00:05:35.250 --> 00:05:37.250
If you don't stay vigilant

00:05:37.860 --> 00:05:40.690
and still dreaming about cooperating
with the Portuguese Macau government

00:05:40.690 --> 00:05:42.090
to investigate the case,

00:05:42.860 --> 00:05:45.790
I'm afraid you will follow the same path
as Mr. Fukue.

00:05:46.540 --> 00:05:47.670
