00:05:48.000 --> 00:05:50.159
who will carry out the task

00:05:50.860 --> 00:05:52.659
the Empire has entrusted to you?

00:05:54.600 --> 00:05:55.430
Well...

00:05:56.390 --> 00:05:58.000
