00:05:58.450 --> 00:05:59.710
Don't worry, Mr. Imai.

00:06:00.660 --> 00:06:02.860
I didn't spend these years in Macau

00:06:03.240 --> 00:06:04.500
for nothing.

00:06:04.770 --> 00:06:06.770
I have already assembled an elite force

00:06:06.770 --> 00:06:08.430
of hundreds of men.

00:06:08.890 --> 00:06:12.190
I will ensure your personal safety.

00:06:14.390 --> 00:06:15.520
That's good to hear.

00:06:15.980 --> 00:06:18.010
Then I'll be relying entirely on you,
Sawa.

00:06:18.010 --> 00:06:20.070
As long as you're willing to trust me,

00:06:20.100 --> 00:06:23.540
you can issue a written notice
to the Portuguese Macau government

00:06:23.540 --> 00:06:24.470
that from now on,

00:06:24.810 --> 00:06:26.980
my Sawa Agency, under your authority,

00:06:27.040 --> 00:06:29.570
will take full control
of the investigation.

00:06:29.630 --> 00:06:30.670
