00:06:34.450 --> 00:06:37.850
Are you truly willing to take on
such a heavy responsibility?

00:06:39.480 --> 00:06:40.270
Mr. Fukue

00:06:40.740 --> 00:06:43.130
was not only a colleague of mine
for many years,

00:06:43.130 --> 00:06:44.690
but also my closest friend.

00:06:46.659 --> 00:06:47.520
And this matter

00:06:47.810 --> 00:06:50.100
also concerns your life and safety.

00:06:52.300 --> 00:06:54.270
Once I have the authority
to handle the case,

00:06:54.270 --> 00:06:55.890
I will uncover the truth,
catch the real culprit,

00:06:55.890 --> 00:06:58.950
and bring the case to light
as quickly as possible.

00:07:01.270 --> 00:07:03.070
I promise you.

00:07:09.600 --> 00:07:10.240
Sawa,

00:07:11.060 --> 00:07:13.130
I'm counting on you then.

00:07:17.120 --> 00:07:18.180
Thank you.

