00:10:24.870 --> 00:10:28.400
the goods would be transported
to the Japanese' own warehouse.

00:10:30.770 --> 00:10:31.870
So now,

00:10:31.870 --> 00:10:33.640
as long as we sail out,

00:10:34.030 --> 00:10:35.750
he'll definitely assume

00:10:35.750 --> 00:10:36.950
the goods are on board

00:10:37.010 --> 00:10:39.010
and then take the bait by chasing us.

