00:11:26.720 --> 00:11:28.250
Since the founding

00:11:28.250 --> 00:11:29.720
of our Tai Ho Brotherhood, in honor of

00:11:29.720 --> 00:11:31.410
the spirit of the Song dynasty's
Prime Minister,

00:11:31.410 --> 00:11:33.030
General Wen,

00:11:33.030 --> 00:11:34.240
our ancestors

00:11:34.530 --> 00:11:36.340
have laid down rules for us to follow:

00:11:36.340 --> 00:11:37.740
every brother of the gang

00:11:37.960 --> 00:11:40.290
must uphold loyalty and honor in jianghu.

00:11:40.910 --> 00:11:42.270
After all these years

00:11:43.390 --> 00:11:44.450
of sailing the seas

00:11:44.770 --> 00:11:46.700
and making our living in the underworld,

00:11:46.700 --> 00:11:47.870
brothers,

00:11:48.530 --> 00:11:50.390
please ask yourselves honestly:

00:11:51.600 --> 00:11:52.510
have we truly

00:11:53.030 --> 00:11:55.790
put loyalty and honor first?

00:12:01.440 --> 00:12:02.640
I'm ashamed to say it,

00:12:03.360 --> 00:12:04.240
but we haven't.

00:12:04.890 --> 00:12:07.050
Including myself, as the Leader,

00:12:07.240 --> 00:12:08.500
sometimes

00:12:08.500 --> 00:12:10.300
