00:12:21.790 --> 00:12:23.600
But in the past few years,

00:12:24.320 --> 00:12:26.040
when we set profit aside,

00:12:26.720 --> 00:12:28.400
stood up for our country and our people,

00:12:28.400 --> 00:12:30.410
and fought against the Japanese,

00:12:30.650 --> 00:12:33.910
only then did we feel
we could finally straighten our backs

00:12:33.930 --> 00:12:36.150
and stand as men with dignity.

00:12:37.200 --> 00:12:39.960
