Captain Huang,

00:25:18.010 --> 00:25:21.270
the goods aren't on the ships.
We didn't find a drop of fuel.

00:25:26.920 --> 00:25:29.900
You youngsters are no match for me.

00:25:31.380 --> 00:25:32.430
Uncle Sanhe,

00:25:33.440 --> 00:25:34.810
rest in peace!

00:26:05.530 --> 00:26:06.400
Idiot!

00:26:09.680 --> 00:26:12.480
The goods
must still be in Rodrigues's warehouse.

00:26:13.160 --> 00:26:15.000
Have the Special Operations Team back
immediately.

00:26:15.000 --> 00:26:15.590
Go!

00:26:24.750 --> 00:26:26.880
Stop! Stop!

00:26:26.880 --> 00:26:28.010
Stop moving!

00:26:28.010 --> 00:26:29.220
Chairman, what's wrong?

00:26:29.220 --> 00:26:32.240
All ships of the Tai Ho Brotherhood

00:26:32.240 --> 00:26:35.090
have been intercepted and destroyed
by the Japanese Army.

00:26:35.090 --> 00:26:36.130
The
Sawa Agency's Special Operations Team's

00:26:36.130 --> 00:26:37.180
speedboats are returning

00:26:37.180 --> 00:26:38.090
and will reach the harbor shortly.

00:26:38.090 --> 00:26:40.590
So they've realized they were fooled.

00:26:40.590 --> 00:26:41.920
Mr. He and the others

00:26:41.920 --> 00:26:44.220
are unloading goods
at the Lyun Coeng warehouse.

00:26:44.220 --> 00:26:46.850
The intelligence agents
will head straight here very soon.

00:26:46.850 --> 00:26:48.240
Leave now.
After you're out of the warehouse,

00:26:48.240 --> 00:26:50.160
make sure to erase the tire tracks

00:26:50.160 --> 00:26:51.740
at the intersection
leading to the Lyun Coeng warehouse.

00:26:51.740 --> 00:26:54.200
Tell them
not to send any more vehicles here.

00:26:54.300 --> 00:26:55.770
But there are traces everywhere,

00:26:55.770 --> 00:26:56.830
inside and outside the warehouse.

00:26:56.830 --> 00:26:58.110
There's no time to clean them all up.

00:26:58.110 --> 00:26:59.740
Once the intelligence agents arrive,

00:26:59.740 --> 00:27:01.500
they'll still figure out
where the goods went.

00:27:01.500 --> 00:27:02.460
Don't worry about here.

00:27:02.460 --> 00:27:03.980
I'll take care of it.

00:27:03.980 --> 00:27:05.940
Chairman, how can you handle it alone?

00:27:05.940 --> 00:27:07.960
Besides, the intelligence agents
will be here soon.

00:27:07.960 --> 00:27:09.660
I've already called the police.

00:27:09.660 --> 00:27:11.940
Inspector General Gonçalves
is on his way here with officers.

00:27:11.940 --> 00:27:13.090
The police will protect me. Go now!

00:27:13.090 --> 00:27:14.570
Go now! Hurry!

00:27:25.250 --> 00:27:25.570
Let's go!

00:27:25.570 --> 00:27:26.830
To Rodrigues' warehouse!

00:27:26.830 --> 00:27:27.760
Yes!

00:27:28.250 --> 00:27:29.070
Get in the car!

00:27:29.070 --> 00:27:29.900
Hurry! Hurry!

00:27:31.200 --> 00:27:32.000
Hurry!

00:28:45.590 --> 00:28:46.200
Yinwan,

00:28:46.200 --> 00:28:47.200
things are too chaotic right now.

00:28:47.200 --> 00:28:48.050
Go back to the hotel first.

00:28:48.050 --> 00:28:49.110
We'll handle the aftermath.

00:28:49.110 --> 00:28:50.050
Be careful then.

00:28:58.110 --> 00:29:01.270
[Department Store]

00:29:01.270 --> 00:29:02.110
Stop the car!

00:29:02.110 --> 00:29:03.090
Stop the car!

00:29:04.270 --> 00:29:05.140
Stop the car!

00:29:06.570 --> 00:29:07.530
Why are you here?

00:29:07.530 --> 00:29:08.880
The intelligence agents are coming.

00:29:08.880 --> 00:29:10.440
The Chairman sent us here

00:29:10.440 --> 00:29:12.310
to stop all empty trucks
that have finished unloading.

00:29:12.310 --> 00:29:14.840
We're not allowed
to return to the warehouse.

00:29:15.290 --> 00:29:16.420
Where's Rodrigues?

00:29:42.600 --> 00:29:43.790
Master Sanhe,

00:29:45.330 --> 00:29:47.590
I should have personally served you tea,

00:29:48.520 --> 00:29:49.850
but there's no tea here.

00:29:53.010 --> 00:29:54.300
So please forgive me

00:29:54.330 --> 00:29:55.530
and follow

00:29:56.070 --> 00:29:57.570
our custom for once.

00:29:57.920 --> 00:30:00.960
Have a sip of wine
from my hometown, Portugal.

00:30:35.860 --> 00:30:36.920
What's that smell?

00:30:36.980 --> 00:30:37.920
-Gasoline?
-Gasoline.

00:30:37.920 --> 00:30:38.780
It's gasoline.

00:30:40.160 --> 00:30:42.690
Rodrigues is trying to destroy
the evidence.

00:30:43.070 --> 00:30:43.730
Rodrigues!

00:30:44.510 --> 00:30:45.740
Put out your lighter.

00:30:47.110 --> 00:30:48.940
Don't think I wouldn't dare touch you

00:30:48.940 --> 00:30:50.800
just because you're a Westerner!

00:30:50.920 --> 00:30:51.790
Right now,

00:30:52.110 --> 00:30:54.350
the Imperial Army
has law enforcement authority in Macau.

00:30:54.350 --> 00:30:56.350
We're carrying out an official duty!

00:30:56.350 --> 00:30:57.970
If you dare set this place on fire,

00:30:57.970 --> 00:31:00.290
I can shoot you dead right now!

00:31:07.030 --> 00:31:08.070
Master Sanhe,

00:31:08.110 --> 00:31:09.860
top-grade Cuban cigars.

00:31:09.890 --> 00:31:12.350
I cherish them
and don't usually smoke them.

00:31:17.050 --> 00:31:17.810
Rodrigues!

00:31:17.940 --> 00:31:18.610
Don't forget,

00:31:18.610 --> 00:31:20.480
you're a Portuguese!

00:31:20.480 --> 00:31:23.240
And the largest Portuguese merchant
in Macau.

00:31:25.570 --> 00:31:28.790
Are you really going to take the fall
for those anti-Japanese rebels

00:31:28.790 --> 00:31:30.660
and burn down your own warehouse?

00:31:34.240 --> 00:31:36.770
There are no Portuguese or Chinese here.

00:31:37.270 --> 00:31:39.920
There is only Rodrigues from Macau.

00:31:41.400 --> 00:31:44.030
And the people of Macau
have only one belief:

00:31:45.010 --> 00:31:47.550
we will never bow our heads.

00:33:45.280 --> 00:33:46.010
Chief.

00:33:46.980 --> 00:33:48.010
The situation is critical.

00:33:48.010 --> 00:33:50.210
The Portuguese police are after us now,

00:33:50.420 --> 00:33:51.540
in large numbers.

00:33:51.610 --> 00:33:53.110
We can't hold them off.

00:33:53.590 --> 00:33:55.740
If the garrison arrives,

00:33:55.900 --> 00:33:57.020
we'll be in real trouble.

00:33:57.020 --> 00:33:58.340
What should we do now?

00:33:58.380 --> 00:33:59.340
Don't panic.

00:34:01.010 --> 00:34:04.410
Take your men and retreat
to the East Asia Hotel immediately.

00:34:04.500 --> 00:34:05.150
What?

00:34:05.640 --> 00:34:06.840
Retreat to the hotel?

00:34:07.290 --> 00:34:08.340
We're retreating to the hotel?

00:34:08.340 --> 00:34:10.070
isn't Consul Imai there?

00:34:10.070 --> 00:34:11.590
Won't everything be exposed?

00:34:11.590 --> 00:34:13.050
It can't be hidden anyway.

00:34:13.420 --> 00:34:15.150
We might as well make it public.

00:34:15.980 --> 00:34:17.330
The bigger the mess, the better.

00:34:17.330 --> 00:34:18.699
Make it so big that Imai can't contain it.

00:34:18.699 --> 00:34:20.170
That will help push the Imperial Army

00:34:20.170 --> 00:34:21.719
to occupy Macau.

00:34:23.560 --> 00:34:25.620
Go all out.

00:34:25.650 --> 00:34:27.250
Even if you tear the roof off,

00:34:28.690 --> 00:34:30.130
I, Sawa Eisaku,

00:34:31.610 --> 00:34:32.889
will cover for you.

00:34:33.070 --> 00:34:33.880
Yes!

00:34:38.570 --> 00:34:40.000
Pass the word.

00:34:40.000 --> 00:34:42.030
Move all weapons and ammunition
stored by the Sawa Agency

00:34:42.030 --> 00:34:43.980
to the East Asia Hotel immediately.

00:34:43.980 --> 00:34:44.460
Yes.

00:35:05.620 --> 00:35:06.420
Master Huang.

00:35:08.800 --> 00:35:10.010
Sir, Mrs. He.

00:35:10.010 --> 00:35:11.210
What's wrong, Zixia?

00:35:11.260 --> 00:35:11.960
Stay at home.

00:35:11.960 --> 00:35:13.590
Don't go anywhere.

00:35:15.090 --> 00:35:16.010
Fei,

00:35:16.370 --> 00:35:17.610
stay here and guard them.

00:35:17.610 --> 00:35:19.750
All other brothers
will come back with me to Haohai.

00:35:19.750 --> 00:35:22.510
Send word by carrier pigeon to all our
branches in the Guangdong–Hong Kong area.

00:35:22.510 --> 00:35:24.500
Assemble all manpower
of the Tai Ho Brotherhood at once

00:35:24.500 --> 00:35:25.630
and head to Macau...

00:35:26.880 --> 00:35:29.410
to avenge the Leader
and our fallen brothers!

