Sawa,

00:37:00.320 --> 00:37:01.780
what's happening outside?

00:37:01.780 --> 00:37:03.670
Why are there suddenly
so many troops and police?

00:37:03.670 --> 00:37:05.880
Mr. Imai, something big has happened.

00:37:06.420 --> 00:37:08.630
The Portuguese Macau government

00:37:10.280 --> 00:37:12.400
is going to openly use force against you.

00:37:12.400 --> 00:37:13.230
Use force?

00:37:13.380 --> 00:37:13.780
Yes.

00:37:14.620 --> 00:37:15.640
Against me?

00:37:26.300 --> 00:37:28.590
Huang Gongjie has led his men

00:37:28.590 --> 00:37:30.380
into the East Asia Hotel.

00:37:30.380 --> 00:37:32.030
The garrison and police
have surrounded the hotel

00:37:32.030 --> 00:37:33.420
to prevent their escape.

00:37:33.420 --> 00:37:36.280
Prevent their escape? At a time like this?

00:37:36.710 --> 00:37:38.530
Why not attack directly?

00:37:38.530 --> 00:37:39.400
Why?

00:37:39.710 --> 00:37:41.760
Exactly.
They even dared to kill Rodrigues.

00:37:41.760 --> 00:37:43.500
What are we waiting for?

00:37:43.500 --> 00:37:46.260
Let's storm in and avenge Rodrigues!

00:37:46.260 --> 00:37:47.920
Everyone, please stay calm.

00:37:47.920 --> 00:37:49.730
We cannot start a fight.

00:37:49.900 --> 00:37:52.860
The Special Operations Team
has not only taken

00:37:52.860 --> 00:37:53.800
all the hotel guests hostage,

00:37:53.800 --> 00:37:54.920
but more importantly,

00:37:54.920 --> 00:37:57.550
Imai and Sawa Eisaku
are also inside the hotel.

00:37:57.760 --> 00:38:00.090
So we can't touch them
because the Japanese are involved?

00:38:00.090 --> 00:38:02.070
Huang Gongjie is nothing
but the Japanese's lackey.

00:38:02.070 --> 00:38:03.090
Rodrigues's blood debt

00:38:03.090 --> 00:38:04.440
should be on the Japanese!

00:38:04.440 --> 00:38:05.650
Why show him any restraint?

00:38:05.650 --> 00:38:08.510
The Special Operations Team is certainly
acting under Sawa Eisaku's orders.

00:38:08.510 --> 00:38:10.570
But the Japanese consul is inside.

00:38:10.570 --> 00:38:11.550
Once fighting starts,

00:38:11.550 --> 00:38:13.320
they'll claim that Macau struck first.

00:38:13.320 --> 00:38:14.590
The Japanese
already have troops at our borders.

00:38:14.590 --> 00:38:16.520
They will seize the chance
to occupy Macau.

00:38:16.520 --> 00:38:17.650
Your Excellency the Governor,

00:38:17.650 --> 00:38:18.800
including you,

00:38:18.800 --> 00:38:20.480
all of our families are still in Macau.

00:38:20.480 --> 00:38:22.340
Even if we don't think of Macau,

00:38:22.340 --> 00:38:23.820
we have to think of our own safety
and that of our families.

00:38:23.820 --> 00:38:25.550
Your Excellency the Governor,

00:38:26.090 --> 00:38:28.150
Inspector General Gonçalves is right.

00:38:28.150 --> 00:38:30.190
We must remain calm now

00:38:30.190 --> 00:38:32.820
and not fire the first shot.

00:38:33.480 --> 00:38:34.510
You Portuguese cowards,

00:38:34.510 --> 00:38:36.340
trying to be spineless again, huh?

00:38:36.340 --> 00:38:37.440
Brothers, let's go ourselves!

00:38:37.440 --> 00:38:38.130
Stop!

00:38:38.340 --> 00:38:39.840
Hurry! Stop them!

00:38:39.840 --> 00:38:40.770
Get out of my way!

00:38:43.440 --> 00:38:44.380
What are you doing?

00:38:44.380 --> 00:38:45.610
Keep being cowards!

00:38:45.610 --> 00:38:46.780
Why are you stopping us?

00:38:46.780 --> 00:38:47.260
I'm telling you,

00:38:47.260 --> 00:38:49.060
my bullets don't discriminate.

00:38:49.150 --> 00:38:49.980
Zixia!

00:38:50.000 --> 00:38:50.800
Master Huang!

00:38:51.280 --> 00:38:52.340
What are you doing?

00:38:52.980 --> 00:38:54.110
What am I doing?

00:38:54.570 --> 00:38:56.110
Huang Gongjie is right in there.

00:38:56.110 --> 00:38:57.440
Uncle and our fallen brothers

00:38:57.440 --> 00:38:59.130
are all waiting for me to avenge them!

00:38:59.130 --> 00:39:01.150
Huang Gongjie's Special Operations Team
numbers two or three hundred.

00:39:01.150 --> 00:39:02.880
Aren't you going to your death?

00:39:03.010 --> 00:39:04.410
Once I pull this trigger,

00:39:04.580 --> 00:39:06.000
it's on.

00:39:06.030 --> 00:39:08.690
These cowards will have to get involved
whether they want to or not!

00:39:08.690 --> 00:39:09.720
Fine, even if they

00:39:09.750 --> 00:39:10.880
keep standing aside,

00:39:10.880 --> 00:39:12.310
the Tai Ho Brotherhood has thousands

00:39:12.310 --> 00:39:13.550
of brothers across all branches.

00:39:13.550 --> 00:39:14.560
I'll call them all here!

00:39:14.560 --> 00:39:16.090
Let's see how he dies today!

00:39:16.730 --> 00:39:17.530
Zixia!

00:39:24.070 --> 00:39:25.600
You know better than anyone

00:39:26.030 --> 00:39:27.830
what Master Sanhe and the others

00:39:27.900 --> 00:39:29.290
died for.

00:39:29.760 --> 00:39:31.440
If you pull the trigger today,

00:39:31.440 --> 00:39:34.480
you'll give the Japanese an excuse
to deploy troops to Macau.

00:39:34.480 --> 00:39:36.300
Then what about those supplies?

00:39:36.480 --> 00:39:37.810
What about all of Macau?

00:39:38.780 --> 00:39:41.570
Wouldn't Master Sanhe
and the others die in vain?

00:39:45.530 --> 00:39:47.000
I understand how you feel.

00:39:48.170 --> 00:39:50.230
We all want revenge for Master Sanhe.

00:39:51.610 --> 00:39:54.070
Huang Gongjie will definitely be punished,

00:39:56.130 --> 00:39:57.320
but not today.

00:40:10.210 --> 00:40:11.130
Rodrigues?

00:40:11.530 --> 00:40:13.460
The son of the former governor of Macau

00:40:13.460 --> 00:40:15.670
and the biggest Portuguese merchant
in Macau?

00:40:15.670 --> 00:40:16.530
They even dared to kill such a

00:40:16.530 --> 00:40:18.210
prominent figure from a neutral country?

00:40:18.210 --> 00:40:18.870
Has your Special Operations Team gone mad?

00:40:18.870 --> 00:40:20.170
[Loyalty, Strength, Success, Morals]

00:40:20.170 --> 00:40:21.360
I told you,

00:40:21.670 --> 00:40:24.210
Rodrigues obstructed
the investigation first.

00:40:24.210 --> 00:40:27.170
The Special Operations Team
only fired warning shots

00:40:27.170 --> 00:40:29.380
and accidentally caused harm.

00:40:29.530 --> 00:40:30.400
But again,

00:40:30.840 --> 00:40:33.230
Rodrigues
colluded with anti-Japanese elements

00:40:33.230 --> 00:40:35.650
to smuggle strategic supplies
for the Chinese Army

00:40:35.650 --> 00:40:37.850
and the Anglo-American Allied Forces.

00:40:38.110 --> 00:40:40.090
He deserved to die anyway.

00:40:41.010 --> 00:40:42.970
And the Portuguese Macau government,

00:40:42.970 --> 00:40:45.680
knowing he was the main culprit
in the major smuggling case,

00:40:45.680 --> 00:40:47.880
still surrounded the Japanese Consul.

00:40:47.980 --> 00:40:50.210
Do you know what that means?

00:40:50.710 --> 00:40:53.880
It's a declaration of war
against the Empire of Japan.

00:40:55.190 --> 00:40:55.900
No.

00:40:56.700 --> 00:40:57.590
The situation isn't clear yet.

00:40:57.590 --> 00:40:58.480
[Loyalty, Strength, Success, Morals]

00:40:58.480 --> 00:41:00.350
We can't jump to that conclusion.

00:41:01.110 --> 00:41:04.970
The Portuguese troops and police
have already surrounded the hotel.

00:41:05.010 --> 00:41:06.780
This is clearly an act of war.

00:41:07.360 --> 00:41:09.120
Even for your personal safety,

00:41:09.320 --> 00:41:10.880
you should report to the Command

00:41:10.880 --> 00:41:11.670
and demand

00:41:12.670 --> 00:41:14.170
the Imperial Army
land in Macau immediately

00:41:14.170 --> 00:41:17.230
to suppress the
Portuguese Macau government by force.

00:41:17.440 --> 00:41:20.090
But the Portuguese haven't fired yet,
have they?

00:41:20.090 --> 00:41:21.090
That means

00:41:21.090 --> 00:41:24.090
they don't want to start a fight.

00:41:24.280 --> 00:41:25.150
Mr. Imai,

00:41:25.530 --> 00:41:28.090
the whereabouts of those
strategic supplies are still unknown.

00:41:28.090 --> 00:41:31.010
They were clearly hidden
by those anti-Japanese elements.

00:41:31.010 --> 00:41:32.570
Once the Imperial Army applies pressure

00:41:32.570 --> 00:41:34.030
and finds them,

00:41:34.380 --> 00:41:36.580
occupying Macau will be fully justified.

00:41:36.580 --> 00:41:37.920
And for you,

00:41:38.050 --> 00:41:40.000
it will be a major achievement.

00:41:41.840 --> 00:41:43.570
And what if we don't find them?

00:41:44.260 --> 00:41:46.530
Wouldn't that mean
I deceived my superiors?

00:41:46.530 --> 00:41:49.000
Then the responsibility would fall on me.

00:41:51.380 --> 00:41:52.420
We will

00:41:53.170 --> 00:41:54.430
definitely find them.

00:41:54.800 --> 00:41:55.920
Colonel Sawa,

00:41:56.730 --> 00:41:59.630
you keep saying
you're helping me investigate the case,

00:41:59.630 --> 00:42:00.480
yet your focus has been entirely

00:42:00.480 --> 00:42:03.480
on some so-called strategic supplies
no one has seen.

00:42:03.480 --> 00:42:05.010
Now the supplies haven't been found,

00:42:05.010 --> 00:42:06.670
Rodrigues has been killed,

00:42:06.670 --> 00:42:09.190
and things have escalated into

00:42:09.190 --> 00:42:11.320
an armed standoff between both sides.

00:42:11.510 --> 00:42:13.370
What exactly are you trying to do?

00:42:13.710 --> 00:42:15.710
I'm only trying to uncover the truth

00:42:16.700 --> 00:42:19.060
behind Fukue's case

00:42:20.360 --> 00:42:21.560
and eliminate

00:42:21.800 --> 00:42:25.050
the anti-Japanese forces
in Macau for the Command.

00:42:25.230 --> 00:42:26.360
Say no more.

00:42:26.730 --> 00:42:28.670
My mission from the Command

00:42:28.860 --> 00:42:30.500
is to uncover the truth of Fukue's murder,

00:42:30.500 --> 00:42:31.830
apprehend the culprit,

00:42:32.000 --> 00:42:35.630
and seek an apology and compensation
from the Portuguese Macau government,

00:42:35.630 --> 00:42:37.230
not to provoke a war.

00:42:38.630 --> 00:42:40.170
The Imperial Army's
current military strength

00:42:40.170 --> 00:42:42.850
does not allow for reckless escalation.

00:42:43.710 --> 00:42:45.770
You two, stay outside and keep watch.

00:42:46.170 --> 00:42:48.840
If anyone fires on the Macao–Portuguese
troops or police on their own initiative

00:42:48.840 --> 00:42:50.340
and attempts
to trigger a military conflict,

00:42:50.340 --> 00:42:51.800
report to me immediately!

00:42:51.940 --> 00:42:52.730
-Yes!
-Yes!

00:42:58.340 --> 00:42:59.240
Colonel Sawa,

00:43:00.150 --> 00:43:02.150
what I need now is direct negotiations

00:43:02.150 --> 00:43:04.690
with the Portuguese Macau government.